description: This Chainlink VRF common Plezier purrs with a rating of 48, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 48, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 5 for East, 3 for South, and 8 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70481-75384-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [48 Votes, Common]
